        "subject": "LU-9613 hsm: fix llog locking in mdt_hsm_pending_restore()",
        "message": "LU-9613 hsm: fix llog locking in mdt_hsm_pending_restore()\n\nThe callback used by mdt_hsm_pending_restore() (hsm_retore_cb())\nmight call llog_write() and therefore should be called with a WRITE\nlock intent.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=sanity-hsm\nSigned-off-by: Quentin Bouget <quentin.bouget@cea.fr>\nChange-Id: I855c7855650a0d2a6f303df0c2e37a34af86bd76\n"
      },
